        <updateDate>2006-08-28T19:06:09Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Expresses the sense of Congress that all students deserve up-to-date textbooks in order to meet national education requirements and that states should ensure that poorer school districts are not deprived of such textbooks.</p> <p>Resolves that primary and secondary schools receive equitable funding for textbooks.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
